===Definitions===
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# to [[cut out]]; to [[cut]] into [[part]]s
#: {{zh-x|裁縫|to tailor ("to cut and sew")}}
#: {{zh-x|裁 衣服|to cut out a garment}}
#* {{zh-x|不知 細 葉 誰 裁 出，二月 春風 似 剪刀。||ref=7th–8th century, {{w|He Zhizhang}}, {{lang|zh|[[s:zh:詠柳 (賀知章)|詠柳]]}}|CL}}
# to [[cut down]]; to [[decrease]]; to [[lay off|lay someone off]]
#: {{zh-x|裁軍|disarmament}}
#: {{zh-x|裁員|to [[lay off]] staff}}
#: {{zh-x|我 被 公司 裁 了。|I got '''laid off''' by my company.}}
# {{lb|zh|literary|or in compounds}} to [[control]]; to [[rule]]
#: {{zh-x|獨裁|authoritarian rule}}
# {{lb|zh|literary|or in compounds}} to [[judge]]; to [[decide]]
#: {{zh-x|裁決|to decide {{q|especially by legal verdict}}}}
#: {{zh-x|仲裁|to arbitrate}}
#: {{zh-x|自裁|to make one's own decision {{q|especially of suicide}}}}
# {{lb|zh|literary|or in compounds}} to [[select]] and [[plan]]
# {{lb|zh|literary|or in compounds}} [[form]] of [[writing]]
#: {{zh-x|體裁|form; style}}
# {{zh-classifier|divisions of standard-size printing paper}}

